{"tid":665754,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[講到口臭] 比先達間黑店搞到部手機燒左","createTime":"2018-05-15T08:41:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T06:17:11.000Z","uid":156666,"like":31,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"feabc03572fe773e141eab371065bf3af062a58a","tid":665754,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T08:41:19.000Z","msg":"原本只係想整番個磨砂Moon貼<br />\n咁去到個間野到 我問佢有冇我呢部機既磨砂Moon貼 佢話&quot;有&quot;<br />\n跟手就問我要唔要整番個立米塗層 然後送個磨砂Moon貼比我<br />\n咁個時我都驚會唔會搞壞我部機<br />\n佢話唔會 仲屌番我傻仔轉頭<br />\n咁你講到咁咪整囉<br />\n過左20分鐘我番黎攞番部機<br />\n佢竟然同我講部機<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">燒左</span><br />\n雖然啲野仲係到但部機黑左一忽 仲要搞到部機而家勁疾<br />\n然後佢叫我比1200佢整番<br />\n<br />\n其實係咪可以報警? 到底佢錯定我錯<br />\n我有咩講唔清楚大家可以問 如果真係佢錯就開名"},{"pid":"d6406f9ea04135a754a43bfca2a36539599b6f72","tid":665754,"uid":30836,"like":57,"dislike":2,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T08:42:24.000Z","msg":"2018都仲有人去先達<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b630f213141e5547ef946a2fe44fd9274a67daf2","tid":665754,"uid":141837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T08:43:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"275f0e0f691e7a49781beef9e2c56d9e2bda6c86","tid":665754,"uid":171958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T08:45:29.000Z","msg":"留名追post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d66bc65c2e535e39f6e08911e6fca8f8b692571b","tid":665754,"uid":56957,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T08:45:52.000Z","msg":"直接屌7佢加報警啦"},{"pid":"23e20ba44e9d68c13a1a5a0e3a908a7da22e46f8","tid":665754,"uid":34927,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T08:47:08.000Z","msg":"愚人節過左一個半月啦樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe6f13af2471d386d79edf38746c07d282a4b89","tid":665754,"uid":186747,"l