faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5cb524f514a5053b0e109cf92a6923a1fefb25","tid":665754,"uid":19979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T04:27:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原本只係想整番個磨砂Moon貼<br />\n咁去到個間野到 我問佢有冇我呢部機既磨砂Moon貼 佢話&quot;有&quot;<br />\n跟手就問我要唔要整番個立米塗層 然後送個磨砂Moon貼比我<br />\n咁個時我都驚會唔會搞壞我部機<br />\n佢話唔會 <span style=\"color: red;\">仲屌番我傻仔轉頭</span><br />\n咁你講到咁咪整囉<br />\n過左20分鐘我番黎攞番部機<br />\n佢竟然同我講部機<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">燒左</span><br />\n雖然啲野仲係到但部機黑左一忽 仲要搞到部機而家勁疾<br />\n然後佢叫我比1200佢整番<br />\n<br />\n其實係咪可以報警? 到底佢錯定我錯<br />\n我有咩講唔清楚大家可以問 如果真係佢錯就開名</blockquote><br />\n紅字佢岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"219ea4cdca98f06a6defd2f926faa102bfb5ff0e","tid":665754,"uid":124107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T04:34:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca2ba194f8015925eb171352b307cd9dd36e0e7f","tid":665754,"uid":9766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T05:50:06.000Z","msg":"可以咁岩有部機無零件而又咁岩係你部機既型號姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無咩既 你都離開過現場範圍先達狗大把理由做得甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}